text: Prices are not transparent leaving you to guess how much is each pastry. Definitely an overpriced shop! First and last time buying from this shop. Asked for this pastry and it was 7.50.. what?

I have no idea what Elizabeth is talking about, this is the best Kopi i had in the area and the price is absolutely fine.

I think she seriously impacted the sales at the shop with that foolish review. Might have been one off incident. It's actually great.
Big cup of local caffeine, tea and other drinks included. Great value!
